'''Ferret Baudoin''' was a writer and a [[Star Wars video games|video game]] designer, and was part of the design team of [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]. He worked for [[Obsidian Entertainment]]. He eventually left the company and went to work for [[BioWare]] and then left them for Bethesda Softworks.

